Package: meanNormalizedUsage
Type: Package
Title: Calculate and Visualize Mean Normalized Usage (MNU) from Cubist Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Meyer P. Bohn [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Meyer P. Bohn <mpbohn@iastate.edu>
Description: Computes the Mean Normalized Usage (MNU) metric based on covariate importance from Cubist models, incorporating both linear model usage and rule-based conditions. Summarizes MNU across multiple soil property models, depths, and covariate groupings for visualization and interpretation of importance.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra,
    stringr
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
BugReports: https://github.com/MollicMeyer/meanNormalizedUsage/issues
URL: https://github.com/MollicMeyer/meanNormalizedUsage
